data.description: **Assumable FHA loan of 3.72% available to qualified buyers** New Roof allowance to buyers at closing. Introducing this lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bath golf course home located in the gated community of Windswept Estates. Discover the allure of its exquisite LVP flooring, expansive open floorplan, recently applied fresh paint, as well as new flooring and doors, a beautiful private office, and custom built-ins in the kitchen pantry and an additional pantry inside the laundry room. This home boasts modern upgrades including a new A/C compressor, a new gas water heater, and a new sprinkler system. Step onto the screened back porch and admire the serene surroundings, while the fenced in backyard provides a private retreat.  There are two propane hookups on the patio to make grilling an ease. Windswept Estates doesn't just offer a home; it also presents a lifestyle. Residents enjoy an array of amenities to include a community pool, clubhouse, pavilion with a BBQ grill, tennis and pickleball courts, basketball facilities, a playground, and even the convenience of weekly food trucks. Special holiday events and scenic walking trails complete this vibrant community. Seize the opportunity to witness all these wonderful features firsthand and schedule your showing today. *Assumable FHA mortgage at 3.72%*
